                    <section id="titles" class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-10 col-lg-offset-2 col-lg-8 print-width-override">
                        <div class="page page-first">
                            <div id="main-titles" class="ornamental-panel">
                                <div class="panel-row">
                                    <div class="title text-bo" lang="bo">ཀླུའི་རྒྱལ་པོ་རྒྱ་མཚོས་ཞུས་པ།</div>
                                </div>
                                <h1 class="panel-row title main-title"><span>The Questions of the Nāga King Sāgara (3)</span></h1>
                                <div class="panel-row">
                                    <div class="title break text-sa" lang="sa-LTN">Sāgara­nāga­rāja­paripṛcchā</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="page">
                            <div id="long-titles">
                                <div class="title text-bo" lang="bo">འཕགས་པ་ཀླུའི་རྒྱལ་པོ་རྒྱ་མཚོས་ཞུས་པ་ཞེས་བྱ་བ་ཐེག་པ་ཆེན་པོའི་མདོ།</div>
                                <div class="title text-wy" lang="bo-LTN">’phags pa klu’i rgyal po rgya mtshos zhus pa zhes bya ba theg pa chen po’i mdo</div>
                                <div class="title text-en" lang="en">The Noble Mahāyāna Sūtra “The Questions of the Nāga King Sāgara”</div>
                                <div class="title break text-sa" lang="sa-LTN">Ārya­sāgara­nāga­rāja­paripṛcchā­nāma­mahā­yana­sūtra</div>
                            </div>
                            <div id="toh">
                                <h3 class="dot-parenth">Toh 155</h3>
                                <p id="location">Degé Kangyur, vol. 58 (mdo sde, pa), folios 205.a–205.b</p>
                                <div class="text-muted">ᴛʀᴀɴsʟᴀᴛᴇᴅ ɪɴᴛᴏ ᴛɪʙᴇᴛᴀɴ ʙʏ</div>
                                <div>
                                    <ul class="list-inline inline-dots">
                                        <li><span>Surendrabodhi</span></li>
                                        <li><span>Yeshé Dé</span></li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>
