                                    <div class="item-content">
                                        <h3><span class="term text-en" lang="en">four aphorisms of the Dharma</span></h3>
                                        <div>
                                            <ul class="list-inline inline-dots">
                                                <li><span class="term text-wy" lang="bo-LTN">chos kyi mdo bzhi</span></li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                        <div>
                                            <ul class="list-inline inline-dots">
                                                <li><span class="term text-bo" lang="bo">ཆོས་ཀྱི་མདོ་བཞི།</span></li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                        <div>
                                            <ul class="list-inline inline-dots">
                                                <li><span class="term text-sa" lang="sa-LTN">dharmoddāna­catuṣṭaya</span></li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="footer">
                                            <p class="definition">The main topic of this sūtra; known also in Tibetan by the synonym <em class="text-wy" lang="bo-LTN">bka’ rtags kyi phyag rgya bzhi</em> (“the <a href="#UT22084-058-002-51" data-glossary-id="UT22084-058-002-51" data-match-mode="matched" class="glossary-link pop-up">four seals</a> of the [Buddha’s] teaching”), in Sanskrit <em class="text-sa" lang="sa-LTN">caturmudrā</em> (“the <a href="#UT22084-058-002-51" data-glossary-id="UT22084-058-002-51" data-match-mode="matched" class="glossary-link pop-up">four seals</a>”) or <em class="text-sa" lang="sa-LTN">dṛṣṭi­nimitta­mudrā</em> (“the seals that are the marks of the [Buddhist] view”).</p>
                                        </div>
